# Proxmox Wazuh SIEM Homelab

## Overview

This project documents the deployment of a self-hosted **Wazuh SIEM/XDR lab** inside my Proxmox homelab.

The goal of this project was to build a practical cybersecurity monitoring environment that can collect endpoint logs, detect security-relevant activity, and provide hands-on experience with SOC-style investigation workflows.

Wazuh was deployed on a dedicated Ubuntu Server VM, and a Wazuh agent was installed on an existing Ubuntu LXC running Grafana, Prometheus, Node Exporter, and Uptime Kuma.

